&lt;li&gt;6+ years of demonstrated leadership experience managing sourcing, procurement, or supply chain organizations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience sourcing critical raw materials, specialty metals, industrial chemicals, advanced materials, or complex manufacturing equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
