&lt;li&gt;Support production equipment installation by ensuring proper mechanical utility integration and system readiness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct field inspections to verify installation quality, safety compliance, and adherence to engineering standards.&lt;/li&gt;
